1. Git running with proxy server 
        first configure the git using:-  
          
          git config --global http.proxy http://proxyUsername:proxyPassword@proxy.server:port
          example git config --global http.proxy http://root:root@172.172.172.31:8008
        
        then use git commands as usual

2. pip running with proxy server 
        
        pip install --proxy=http://proxyUsername:proxyPassword@proxy.server:port packagename
        example  pip install --proxy=http://root:root@172.172.172.31:8008 numpy
        
